        .span3.hidden-phone
          .well.sidebar-nav
            .nav-list
              %h2 Hey Marseilles
              %h4 Lines We Trace Tour 2013
              %p
                Trailer Swift is the name of our trailer. 
                %a{:href => "http://heymarseilles.com"} Lines We Trace 
                is the brand new album we released 3/5/13. 
                Follow our route around the country and catch a show if you can.
            %ul.nav.nav-list.tour-dates
